{"tid":2167951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警拘一名26歲男子 檢值近5百萬毒品及製毒工具","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T12:51:47.000Z","uid":135488,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7eea2407776b4cc86745cc555da5bcd064a44823","tid":2167951,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:15:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545026-20200821.htm       \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545026-20200821.htm%20%20%20%20%20%20%20&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=583ba302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545026-20200821.htm%20%20%20%20%20%20%20&h=e7d9748e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545026-20200821.htm       </a><br />\n警方在馬鞍山一個單位，搜出一批製毒用原材料，並檢獲約值498萬元的毒品，26歲男子被控以製毒，上午在沙田裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，昨日下午在馬鞍山恆明街附近截查一名目標男子，其後帶他去到區內一個屋苑的單位搜查，檢獲約3公升液態可卡因以及約503克懷疑霹靂可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n警員亦在單位內，發現有梳打粉、亞司通及一批製毒工具，相信有人將可卡因混入紅酒，企圖掩人耳目，以提煉方式將液態可卡因凝固，再包裝成製成品出售。"},{"pid":"ea5252a1982da8008883827883e60288ca3b2945","tid":2167951,"uid":135488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"以為自己breaking bad咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc82b56349701c838036936d0fef957299fa4f5","tid":2167951,"uid":63670,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:18:47.000Z","msg":"無交保護費<br />\n或者無俾pk抽佣<br />\n所以咪捉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaddff494f766a9ff71ed9b840ac3743accd9f16","tid":2167951,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc82b56349701c838036936d0fef957299fa4f5","tid":2167951,"uid":63670,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:18:47.000Z","msg